short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Removes the feed from Youtube, Instagram and Amazon, so that you can browse distraction free

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
UnInternet redesigns the web! 
If you're addicted to the internet or want to be able to focus more, this one's for you.

Youtube no longer has feed, shorts or explore. Youtube now has a centered search bar along with that things you actually need. 

Instagram no longer has stories, reels, feed or threads.

Amazon isn't ugly anymore! 
It's UI has been overhauled. It now has a centered search bar and all unnecessary information has been cleaned up.

UnInternet is a package of UnYoutube, UnInstagram and UnAmazon.
(Previously known as Thrive)
